{"tid":1940443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幫推thx】和你登記做選民 & 立會要初選「三不投」聯署","createTime":"2020-03-23T18:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T00:08:13.000Z","uid":141286,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0962e84d92655fcabc6809409413efde0e44e9","tid":1940443,"uid":141286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T18:57:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和你登記做選民</span></span><br />\n凡登記DSE考生必考靚Grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">選民登記填表機（快靚正）</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1hVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=897a4b1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote</a><br />\n<br />\n選民資料網上查閱系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1hVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=8648b6b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">只要在2020年7月25日或以前年滿18歲，今年5月2日前可登記做選民\n\n18歲生日快樂 即刻登記做選民</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】</span></strong></span><br />\nFB Link<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.me/legcopetition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Flegcopetition&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1hVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=2f4f7858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.me/legcopetition</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">聯署link：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf--3WrL03pxfJALAgIAMIarSqyBNrbfTYFVZaxafm8wmt23Q/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSf--3WrL03pxfJALAgIAMIarSqyBNrbfTYFVZaxafm8wmt23Q%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1hVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=b2fd6698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf--3WrL03pxfJALAgIAMIarSqyBNrbfTYFVZaxafm8wmt23Q/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署三點：<br />\n呼籲香港選民，於2020年立法會選舉，不投票給以下三種參選人：<br />\n（1）反對舉行初選/協調的，不投！<br />\n（2）有初選/協調機制但不參與的，不投！<br />\n（3）初選落選後不肯退選或協調組隊的，不投！<br />\n<br />\n原po<br />\n【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】進度匯報 + 需要大家幫忙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1940299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1940299</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"87df18ca47c2abcf207be53783e1fdc696a07bf4","tid":1940443,"uid":141286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:04:59.000Z","msg":"另可選擇填寫選民登記表格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可循以下途徑索取表格：<br />\n1。各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1hVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=ea990eed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n2。公共屋邨辦事處（大家樓下就有）<br />\n3。選舉事務處地址：<br />\n-&gt;香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓<br />\n-&gt;九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓"},{"pid":"399c748a9fcc91b3cfda179fb514698f3aca9ce2","tid":1940443,"uid":141286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/75XjnXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75XjnXd.jpg&h=5bfa9f32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80ed864e33cc23fc3101aeab63a674906a774e3d","tid":1940443,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2624a5d2d907a74c59efc26774d79c69cec4bea","tid":1940443,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d0962e84d92655fcabc6809409413efde0e44e9","tid":1940443,"uid":141286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl